des:
Delta Children Connect help you control your Delta Smart Music Module from bassinet.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off and adjust volume , dim night light, adjust auto glider speed for 
Delta Smart Music Module.

There’s no need to go to the buttons to adjust volume , dim night light, adjust auto glider speed for 
Delta Smart Music Module - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to Delta Children Connect in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Delta Children Connect" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Delta Children Connect account in our " Delta Children Connect" app;
(3). You need to have some Delta Children Connect devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Delta Children Connect" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Delta Children Connect" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Delta Children Connect" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Delta Children Connect", and you'll be navigated to Delta Children Connect login page;
(9). Input Delta Children Connect account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on Delta light.”
“Alexa,turn off Delta light”
“Alexa,brighten the Delta light.”
“Alexa,dim the Delta light.”
“Alexa,set Delta light to 50%.”
“Alexa,set Delta light to blue.”
“Alexa,set Delta light to cool white.”
